quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  38,43,"“Ndipo tidamubwezera anthu ake, ndi kumpatsanso ena onga iwo (m’kuchuluka kwawo) powaphatikiza ndi omwe adali nawo; (tidachita zimenezi) chifukwa cha chifundo chochokera kwa Ife ndi kuti chikhale chikumbutso kwa eni nzeru"
  38,44,““Ndipo gwira m’dzanja lako mtolo wa zikoti; menya ndi mtolowo ndipo usaswe lonjezo.” Ndithu Ife tidampeza ali wopirira. Taonani kukhala bwino kapolo! Ndithu iye ngotembenukira kwambiri kwa Allah
  38,45,"“Kumbukira, (iwe Mtumiki {s.a.w}) akapolo athu Ibrahim, Ishâq ndi Ya’qub, eni mphamvu (pa ntchito yachipembedzo) ndi kuyang’ana kozindikira"
  38,46,“Ndithu Ife tidawasankha powapatsa chikhalidwe chabwino (chomwe) ndi kukumbukira Nyumba yomaliza (nthawi zonse)
  38,47,“Ndithu kwa Ife iwo adali mwa anthu abwino omwe adasankhidwa
  38,48,"“Ndipo kumbuka Ismail, Alyasa’ (Eliya), ndi Thulkifl (Yesaya); ndipo onsewo adali mwa anthu abwino"
  38,49,“Ichi ndichikumbutso (kwa iwe ndi anthu ako). Ndipo ndithu oopa Allah ali ndi mabwelero abwino
  38,50,“(Awakonzera iwo) minda yamuyaya yotsekulidwa makomo ake kwa iwo
  38,51,"“(Azidzakhala m’menemo) uku atatsamira (makama amtengo wapatali, ndipo adzakhala akusangalala) akuitanitsa mmenemo zipatso ndi zakumwa zambiri"
  38,52,"“Ndipo (ku Munda wamtenderewo) adzakhala ndi akazi oyang’ana amuna awo okha basi, ofanana misinkhu"
  38,53,“Izi ndi zomwe mukulonjezedwa pa tsiku la chiweruziro
  38,54,“Ndithu izi ndizopatsa Zathu zosatha
  38,55,"“Awa ndimalipiro (a oopa Allah)! Koma opyola malire (ndi kunyoza aneneri awo), ali ndi mabwelero oipa"
  38,56,“(Omwe ndi) Jahannam adzailowa (ndi kupseleramo). Taonani kuipa kwa malo wokakhazikikamo
  38,57,"“Awa ndimadzi wotentha kwambiri, ndi mafinya (a anthu a ku Moto). Choncho awalaweko"
  38,58,“Ndi zilango zina zambiri zonga zimenezi zamitundumitundu
  38,59,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa opyola malire, omwe ndiatsogoleri a opembedza mafano): “Gulu ili lalikulu, lilowa nanu ku Moto; (omwe adali okutsatirani. Ndipo atsogoleri adzati): Siolandiridwa (mwamtendere). Ndithu iwo ngolowa ku Moto.”"
  38,60,"“(Otsatira adzanena): “Ndithu tembeleroli likuyenera inu, (limene mukutitembelera ife) chifukwa inu ndiamene mudadzetsa chilangochi potinyenga ife (ndi kutiitanira kunjira yopotoka), taonani kuipa malo okhazikikamo (Jahannam)!”"
  38,61,"“(Otsatira) adzanena: “E Mbuye wathu! Muonjezereni chilango ku Moto pamwamba pa chilango amene watidzetsera chilangochi.”"